                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Schraml, B. U., Hildner, K., Ise, W. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">The AP-1 transcription factor Batf controls T<sub>H</sub>17 differentiation.</span> <span class='so'>Nature, 460, 405-409 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19578362" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Betz, B. C., Jordan-Williams, K. L., Wang, C. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Batf coordinates multiple aspects of B and T cell function required for normal antibody responses.</span> <span class='so'>J. Exp. Med., 207, 933-942 (2010)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20421391" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>King, C.</span>: <span class="ti">New insights into the differentiation and function of T follicular helper cells.</span> <span class='so'>Nat. Rev. Immunol., 9, 757-766 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19855402" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Nurieva, R. I., Chung, Y., Martinez, G. J. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Bcl6 Mediates the development of T follicular helper cells.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 325, 1001-1005 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19628815" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Johnston, R. J. Poholek, A. C., DiToro, D. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Bcl6 and Blimp-1 are reciprocal and antagonistic regulators of T follicular helper cell differentiation.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 325, 1006-1010 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19608860" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Yu, D., Rao, S., Tsai, L. M. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">The transcriptional repressor Bcl-6 directs T follicular helper cell lineage commitment.</span> <span class='so'>Immunity, 31, 457-468 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub